short_bio: Jenny Smith is a classically trained chef who specializes in French cuisine. She worked at several Michelin-starred restaurants in Paris before moving to New York to open her own restaurant.
Juan Saha is a Mexican chef who draws inspiration from his mother's cooking. He has worked at several high-end restaurants in Mexico City and now owns a popular taqueria in Los Angeles.
Ema chyd is a Chinese-American chef who specializes in fusion cuisine. She has worked in some of the top restaurants in San Francisco and now runs her own pop-up restaurant.
Mohammed Ali is an Egyptian chef who is passionate about Middle Eastern cuisine. He has worked at several restaurants in Cairo and now owns a popular Middle Eastern restaurant in London.
Md Mahbubul Alom is a Korean-American chef who specializes in Korean fusion cuisine. She has worked at some of the top restaurants in Los Angeles and now runs her own food truck.
Md. Mahadi Hasan is a Mexican chef who specializes in regional cuisine from Oaxaca. He has worked at several top restaurants in Mexico and now owns a popular Mexican restaurant in Chicago.
Md Bariul Islam is a Korean chef who is passionate about traditional Korean cuisine. She has worked at some of the top restaurants in Seoul and now owns a popular Korean restaurant in New York City.
